{"tid":1561040,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"沙田跳閘好撚多籃屍","createTime":"2019-09-11T12:31:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-11T18:46:15.000Z","uid":158067,"like":707,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":114,"replies":[{"pid":"219d34793f9d9435f294d223aedda9638ee9ac6e","tid":1561040,"uid":158067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T12:31:17.000Z","msg":"見到好多手足跳沙田，仲要diu 鳩埋條肥佬籃屍，不過小心啲。<br />\n眼見差唔多10隻仆街捉跳閘。<br />\n一隻紅色衫，四眼肥鳩。<br />\n一隻白色衫，白頭髮老坑。<br />\n二至三隻灰衫，好撚大隻，其中一隻手臂有紋身。<br />\n仲有幾隻，睇唔清楚。<br />\n手足跳完即走，唔好戀戰。"},{"pid":"662517893151d5400a97df66b86a873a41ebd3f3","tid":1561040,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T12:31:52.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"0079fbad056c7367fd6d8155b25fbacd687317e5","tid":1561040,"uid":158067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T12:31:53.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"ba66c40f6836882ed99edf100631d5cdaf4bf162","tid":1561040,"uid":38109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T12:32:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/